**Reading the diagram:**
- `HermesLifecycle` (yellow) remains the sole writer of the phase value.
- `Hermes.ts` (blue, bold) is the orchestrator. It composes Lifecycle + Registry + HealthMonitor + EventDispatcher + PluginLoader + Config and exposes the public `Hermes` API.
- Every component has a single owner. No sibling-to-sibling wiring except via the façade.
- `@agent-os/observability` is shown dashed — reserved for future Bootstrap integration; not yet wired.
